    skos:prefLabel "Perceptions are organized into a hierarchy of concepts dependent on collective systems of knowledge. norms. values and beliefs. which in turn guide cultural. governance and land management practices. as well as resource use and consumer behaviours. Taken together. these elements constitute a world view." .

